snippet.title: Brother Vs Sister Roblox Challenge
snippet.description:
Today I challenge my sister in Roblox. #Roblox is a fun free game! 

This game is also available on Android and its free to download! My sister plays this game on her Android Tab everyday and she thinks she can defeat me in a Roblox battle
I am an Android Lover 😎 and I have played lot of Android Games so I am Pro at this and I will definitely win this match! Gaming is smooth on Android because Game Mode Rocks 💯 Happy to be part of Team Android 😎 Suggest me some more android games to play in my next videos!

Roblox is a really fun game in which you can play different games for free. Roblox is a free game and today me and my sister challenge eachother in Roblox. If she wins then she gets 10000 Robux
Hope you enjoy this video.

my insta - https://www.instagram.com/mythpat

#gaming #mythpat

snippet.description:
#ରାତି_୧୧ଟା_ବେଳେ_କିଏ_ଆସିଥିଲା ?
ଆର.ଜି କର ମେଡିକାଲ କଲେଜ ଡାକ୍ତରୀ ଛାତ୍ରୀ ମୃତ୍ୟୁ ମାମଲାରେ ସିବିଆଇର ବଡ ଖୁଲାସା। ରାତି ୧୧ଟା ବେଳେ ଏମିତି ହୋଇଥିଲା କ’ଣ? କିଏ ଡାକ୍ତରଖାନା ଭିତରକୁ ପ୍ରବେଶ କରିଥିଲେ? ଅଘଟଣ ରାତିରେ ବାସ୍ତବରେ ହୋଇଥିଲା କ’ଣ? ଦେଖନ୍ତୁ ଏହି ରିପୋର୍ଟ ।

snippet.title: B Praak - Mukke Paye Si | Sunny Kaushal | Neha Sharma | Sagar | Bunny | Arvvindr S Khaira
snippet.description:
B Praak returns to Desi Melodies with the soul-stirring, "Mukke Paaye Si." It is a story featuring Sunny Kaushal and Neha Sharma of lost love along with the lingering pain it leaves behind, resonating with anyone who has felt the ache of a broken heart and reminding us of the strength required to endure a heartbreak. 

Listen to 'Mukke Paye Si' on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/MPS

snippet.title: 300 Kg WHOLE BEEF PICKLE | Indian Kerala Beef Pickle Recipe | Village Cooking
snippet.description: Today we made a spicy Buffalo pickle in our Village . First we brought a whole buffalo . We made it into small pieces after a proper cleaning. Then we marinate the buffalo with spicy masalas and deep fried it in the aromatic coconut oil. Then the preparation of spicy and tasty pickle starts with the traditional method. You can check it out here for the village style recipes .

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.title: RG Kar Live: আরজি কর কাণ্ডে ধৃত সঞ্জয় ঘটনার দিন হাসপাতালে তিনবার এসেছিল , চাঞ্চল্যকর তথ্য CBI সূত্রে
snippet.description:
ABP Ananda Live: আর জি কর মেডিক্যালে মহিলা চিকিৎসক ধর্ষণ-খুনে অভিযুক্ত সঞ্জয় সম্পর্কে নতুন তথ্য। ঘটনার দিন হাসপাতালে তিনবার এসেছিল সঞ্জয়, খবর সিবিআই সূত্রে। প্রথমবার সঞ্জয় আর জি কর হাসপাতালে ঢোকে সন্ধে ৬টায়, খবর সূত্রের। সঞ্জয়ের সঙ্গে ছিল সৌরভ নামে এক সিভিক ভলান্টিয়ার, খবর সিবিআই সূত্রে। সিভিক ভলান্টিয়ার সৌরভের দাদা ভর্তি ছিল আর জি কর হাসপাতালের সার্জারি ওয়ার্ডে। 

আরও খবর, আরও খবর, আন্দোলনকারীদের আক্রমণ করতে গিয়ে এবার মহিলাদের কেশসজ্জা নিয়ে কটাক্ষ তৃণমূলের মন্ত্রীর। 'যাঁদের বয় কাট চুল বা যাঁরা চুল স্ট্রেট করেন, তাঁরা মদের বিরুদ্ধে প্রতিবাদ করেন না'। 'তাঁরা মদ খান না, তাঁরা ড্রিঙ্ক করেন'। মন্তব্য উত্তরবঙ্গ উন্নয়নমন্ত্রী উদয়ন গুহর। মহিলাদের জিন্স পরা নিয়েও কটাক্ষ উদয়নের। বাংলাদেশ প্রসঙ্গ টেনেও আন্দোলনকারীদের হুঁশিয়ারি উত্তরবঙ্গ উন্নয়নমন্ত্রী। 'হাসিনাকে দেখে যাঁদের মুখে হাসি ফুটেছে, তা কী করে বন্ধ করতে হয়, তৃণমূল জানে'। 'এই কথা মাথায় রেখে সাবধানে আন্দোলন এগিয়ে নিয়েও যাও'। 'কিন্তু নৈরাজ্য সৃষ্টি করতে চাইলে, তা প্রতিহত করার রাস্তা জানা আছে'। হুঙ্কার উত্তরবঙ্গ উন্নয়নমন্ত্রী উদয়ন গুহর। 

#CBI #Sanjayray #RGKarMedicalCollege #RGKarMedicalStudentDeath #RGKarStudentDeath #KolkataMedicalStudentDeath #ABPAnanda #BanglaNews #banglanewslive #ABPAnanda #Bengalinews #ABPAnandaDigital #ABPAnandaLIVE #BengaliNews #এবিপিআনন্দ #এবিপিআনন্দলাইভ #এবিপিআনন্দ #এবিপিআনন্দলাইভ

___________

আপনার পছন্দের খবর আর আপডেট পাবেন আপনার পছন্দের চ্যাটিং প্ল্যাটফর্ম হোয়াটস অ্যাপেও। যুক্ত হোন ABP Ananda হোয়াটস অ্যাপ চ্যানেলে।

𝐌: હે એક દાડો યુગ જેવડો કાઢવો મારે ચો
𝐅: હે હેડો મારી હંગાથ માં હાહરે કોક દાડો રો
𝐌: હે હુ તો મજાક, મજાક કરું મારી માનતી જઈ આવો તમે જો

𝐌: He Prero Tame Per, Pero Odho Ne Parvaro Na Cho Kau Shu Kaya

𝐌: He Haga Vala Ke Vahu Bahu Hari

𝐅: He Tamara Ne Amara Mavtar Juda Ganya Se Me Cho

𝐌: હે હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદીયો પરવાર્યા શો ચો
     હે તમે હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદીયો પરવાર્યા શો ચો
     હે ફરો અલગ તમે મુડ માં અમને કોક તો કો
𝐅: હે ટોનટ ના મારો શાંતિ તમે રાખો
     પરવાર તો ચો હજી કરીયો મેં આખો 
𝐌: કાજળ ભરેલી તારી કાળી કાળી આંખો
      સૂરજ ને પણ એ કરી નાખે જોખો
𝐅: હે બાર મહિના થી કરુ ધહાણી પેર્યુ ઓઢિયુ કોઈ ચો
𝐌: હે પેરો તમે પેરો, પેરો ઓઢો ને પરવારો ના ચો કઉ શુ કયા...

𝐅: હો તૈયાર થઈ ને તમે ફરો બાર મહિના
     અમે આજ પરવારા તો ડોળા ઘાઢો કઈના 
𝐌: જા જા જુઠી હોંભળયા હમાચર બુન ને જમાઈ ના
      એટલે નાહિ જાવુ તારે ઘરે તારા ભાઈ ના
𝐅: હો પોર આઠમ ના ટોણે આવુજ કરીયુ તુ 
     દાબ બતાવી મારજો અમે માડી વાલ્યુ તુ
𝐌: હે હગા વાલા કે વહુ બહુ હારી
      તે મારા બાની સેવા ઘણી કરી 
𝐅: હે તમારા ને મારા માવતર જુદા ગણ્યા સે મે ચો
𝐌: એટલે તો કહુ છુ મારી વાલી ઘડીએ દૂર ના થો...

𝐅: હો ફોન કરી ને બુન ને તેડાયા સે અમે
    ટોનટ મારવા ના ખોટા રેવાદો ને તમે
𝐌: હે વાલી મારી હાચે હાચુ કહીદુ હમ ખઈ ને માના
      તારા વગર ચાલતુ નથી એટલે કરું બાના
𝐅: હો એટલે તો કઉ છુ શાંતિ તમે રાખો
     તમને પડવા નહિ દુ કોઈ વખો
𝐌: હે યાદ આવે આ તારા વાલાપ ની વાતો
      દાડો તો જાય પણ જાતી નથી રાતો
𝐅: હે વાલા આજે સાતમ તો હેડી કાલ નો દાડો રયો
𝐌: હે એક દાડો યુગ જેવડો કાઢવો મારે ચો
𝐅: હે હેડો મારી હંગાથ માં હાહરે કોક દાડો રો
𝐌: હે હુ તો મજાક, મજાક કરું મારી માનતી જઈ આવો તમે જો
      વળજો વેલા હર... 

📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: English  👇

𝐌: He Hathe Meli Lal Mehandiyo Parvaya Sho Cho
   He Tame Hathe Meli Lal Mehandiyo Parvaya Sho Cho
   He Faro Tame Alag Mud Ma Amane Kok To Ko
𝐅: He Tonat Na Maro Shanti Tame Rakho
    Parvar To Haji Karyo Chaya Me Aakho
𝐌: Kajal Bhareli Tari Kali Kali Aankho
     Suraj Ne Pan Ae Kari Nakhe Jokho
𝐅: He Bar Mahina Thi Karu Gharni Peryu Odhiyu Koi Cho
𝐌: He Prero Tame Per, Pero Odho Ne Parvaro Na Cho Kau Shu Kaya

𝐅: Ho Taiyar Thai Ne Tame Faro Bar Mahina
    Ame Aaje Parvara To Dola Ghadho Kaina 
𝐌: Ja Ja Tuthi Hombhala Hamachar Bun Ne Jamani Na
     Aetale Nahi Javu Tare Ghare Tara Bhai Na
𝐅: Ho Por Aatham Na Dade Aavuj Karyu Tu 
    Dab Manjo Ame Madi Valyu Tu
𝐌: He Haga Vala Ke Vahu Bahu Hari
     Te Mara Bani Seva Ghani Kari 
𝐅: He Tamara Ne Amara Mavtar Juda Ganya Se Me Cho
𝐌: Aetle To Kahu Chhu Mari Vali Ghadiae Dur Na Tho

𝐅: Ho Phone Kari Ne Bun Ne Tedaya Se Amese
    Tonat Marava Na Khota Revado Ne Tame
𝐌: He Vali Mari Hache Hachu Kahidu Ham Khai Ne Mana
     Tara Vagar Chaltu Nathi Aetle Karu Bana
𝐅: Ho Aetle kau Chhu Shanti Tame Rakho
    Tamne Padva Nahi Du Koi Vakho
𝐌: He Yad Aave Se Tara Valap Ni Aa Vato
     Dado To Jay Pan Jati Nathi Rato
𝐅: He Vala Aaje To Satam Hedi Kal No Dado Rayo
𝐌: He Ek Dado Yug Jevado Kadhavo Mare Cho
𝐅: He Hedo Mari Hangath Ma Hahare Kok Dado Ro
𝐌: He Huto Majak, Majak Karu Mari Maniti Jai Aavo Tame Jo
     Valjo Vela Har

Kaffara Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 18th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
Celebrate 78th Independence Day and immerse yourself in the soul-stirring sounds of "Vande Mataram" as A.R. Rahman brings to life the spirit of India with his timeless anthem, "Maa Tujhe Salaam." Penned by Mehboob and composed by the maestro himself, this song has become a symbol of national pride and unity.

Song Name – Maa Tujhe Salaam 
Music – A.R. Rahman
Lyrics – Mehboob Kotwal
Producer & Director – Bharat Bala

Rabb ne jatti ch jatta paa ke bhejya 
Ucha kadd uchhi heel uchha nakhra
Haan rabb ne jatti ch jatta paa ke bhejya

Kadd de karod ke je gaal balliye
Oh wadda dil wadde note caran waddiyan
Jammeya jattan de putt naal balliye
Wadda dil wadde note caran waddiyan
Jammeya jattan de putt naal balliye


Ve onu fer theke aali paani lagdi
Jinnu nasha jatti de pyar da jatta
Parcheya di century ve maari firda
Koka mera 90 ko hazaar da jatta
Kaptaan kaptaan naam suneya hou
Menu jide lekhan ch likha ke bhejya
Ve ucha kadd uchhi heel uchha nakhra
Rabb ne jatti ch jatta paa ke bhejya 
Ucha kadd uchhi heel uchha nakhra

Sapniya rakhaan keel keel jattiye

snippet.title: World’s Deadliest Battle | The Mahabharat Series | Ep 1 | Vikram Aditya  | Telugu
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first episode in our series on the Mahabharat, one of the greatest epics ever written. In this drama, we delve into the profound truth that there are no purely good or bad people, only good and bad circumstances.
In this episode, we explore Vyasa's visionary experience that led to the creation of this timeless epic. Discover how Vyasa, after dividing the Vedas, received a haunting vision of a catastrophic war—The Mahabharat. Disturbed and eager to document every detail, Vyasa chose the only being capable of keeping up with his narration, Lord Ganesha, to write down the untold story of his descendants.
Our storytelling is not just about revisiting ancient tales; it's about extracting timeless wisdom to confront modern challenges. This episode lays the foundation for understanding the Mahabharat's depth, where virtue and vice intertwine, revealing critical life lessons.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:

Song: Raksha Bandhan (Title Track)
Music: Himesh Reshammiya
Lyrics: Irshad Kamil
Singer: Shreya Ghoshal
Music Programmers: Suhas Parab, Subhash Parab, Priyesh Vakil, Barzin Contractor & Pratik Panchal
Guitar: Chintoo Singh Wazir
Flute: Kiran Vinkar
Sitar: Sweekar Katti 
Bela Bahar: Naviin Gandharv
Sound Engineers: Salman Shaikh and Anudutt Shamain at HR Musik Studio
Mixed and Mastered by: Salman Shaikh and Anudutt Shamain at HR Musik Studio
HR Musik Creative Team: Rahul Sheth, Rajendra Toraskar, Prakash Serrao, Ravi Desai

Zee Studios In Association with Alka Hiranandani And Aanand L Rai Present
A Colour Yellow Production In Association With Cape Of Good Films
A Film By - Aanand L Rai 
Produced By - Aanand L Rai, Himanshu Sharma
Written By - Himanshu Sharma & Kanika Dhillon 
Co-Producer - Kanupriya A Iyer & Vedant Baali
Choreographer - Vijay Ganguly

Lyrics: 
पहली यारी तुमसे मेरी 
पहला गुस्सा तुमसे था 
भाई मेरे बचपन का तो 
पूरा किस्सा तुमसे था 

Pehli Yaari Tumse Meri
Pehla Gussa Tumse Tha
Bhai Mere Bachpan Ka Toh
Poora Kissa Tumse Tha

आधा हिस्सा था वो मेरा 
आधा हिस्सा तुमसे था 
भाई मेरे बचपन का तो 
पूरा किस्सा तुमसे था 

Aadha Hissa Tha Woh Mera
Aadha Hissa Tumse Tha
Bhai Mere Bachpan Ka Toh
Poora Kissa Tumse Tha

रक्षाबंधन वादा है 
या धागा है प्यार का 
ओ...धागा है प्यार का 

Rakshabandhan Vaada Hai
Ya Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 
O… Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 

थोड़ा सा है चंदन 
छोटा सा है टीका 
बंधन जिंदगी का 

Thoda Sa Hai Chandan
Chhota Sa Hai Teeka
Bandhan Zindagi Ka

रक्षाबंधन वादा है 
या धागा है प्यार का 
ओ...धागा है प्यार का 

Rakshabandhan Vaada Hai
Ya Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 
O… Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 

सात रंग सच्चे सभी 
कब हुए हैं कच्चे कभी 
देखने को नाज़ुक हैं पर 
टूटते ना डोरियाँ 

Saat Rang Sachche Sabhi 
Kab Hue Hai Kachche Kabhi 
Dekhne Ko Nazuk Hai Par 
Tootate Na Doriyan 

चाहतों की झांकी मिले 
चिट्ठियों में राखी मिले 
भूलती कभी ना बहनें 
हो हज़ारों दूरियाँ

Chaahaton Ki Jhaanki Mile 
Chitthiyon Mein Rakhi Mile
Bhulti Kabhi Na Behne 
Ho Hazaron Dooriyan

रक्षाबंधन वादा है 
या धागा है प्यार का 
ओ...धागा है प्यार का 

Rakshabandhan Vaada Hai
Ya Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 
O… Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 

मां की एक परछाई सी 
बहन में दिखाई देती है 
और पिता नजर आते है 
भाईयों की बात में  

Maa Ki Ek Parchhaayi Si
Behen Mein Dikhaayi Deti
Aur Pita Nazar Aate Hai
Bhaiyon Ki Baat Mein

खून का ये रिश्ता भी है, 
है जुबां का नाता भी, 
मान जो लिया भाई तो 
सांस-सांस साथ में 

Khoon Ka Yeh Rishta Bhi Hai
Hai Zubaan Ka Naata Bhi
Maan Jo Liya Bhai Toh
Saans-Saans Saath Mein

रक्षाबंधन वादा है 
या दावा है प्यार का 
ओ...दावा है प्यार का 

Rakshabandhan Vaada Hai
Ya Daava Hai Pyaar Ka 
O… Daava Hai Pyaar Ka 

थोड़ा सा है रेशम 
थोड़ा सा है मीठा 
बंधन ज़िंदगी का
Thoda Sa Hai Resham 
Thoda Sa Hai Meetha 
Bandhan Zindagi Ka

रक्षाबंधन वादा है 
या धागा है प्यार का 
ओ...धागा है प्यार का 

Rakshabandhan Vaada Hai
Ya Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka 
O… Dhaaga Hai Pyaar Ka

snippet.title: Discussion के बीच किसे देख कर उड़ गए Bhide के होश? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 17 Aug 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

When Roshan refuses to let Sodhi inside the house, Sodhi stays over at Mehta’s place for the night. However, when Sodhi tries to apologize to Roshan in the morning, she declines his apology. So, Sodhi climbs up a terrace wall and threatens to kill himself if Roshan does not let him in the house. What will Roshan do now? 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 85
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G3llgXXAQTJN4XEjiZb2d0q

snippet.title: Mahindra Thar Roxx 5 door - Every Detail | AutoYogi | ICN Studio
snippet.description: Mahindra Thar’s 5-door version - Roxx - was finally launched in India on the evening of India’s 77th Independence Day. Similar to the 3-door version, it’s based on the same Scorpio N platform but several changes has been made to it to accommodate an extra row of seats and a bigger boot. The vehicle’s cabin too has seen an overhaul as it receives a revised dashboard layout that now accommodates a new 10.25-inch touchscreen, a 10.25-inch instrument cluster screen, soft touch material on top of the dash, a 360 degree camera, ventilated seats, electrically-adjustable driver seat, auto-dimming IRVM, panaromic sunroof, harmon-kardon music system, wireless charger, wireless apple carplay and android auto among others. So far we only know the prices of its base variants, the petrol base costs Rs 12.99 lakh (ex-showroom) and the diesel base costs Rs 13.99 lakh (ex-showroom). More details on its performance will be updated on 17th August. Stay tuned for that.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta | UEFA Super Cup 2024
snippet.description:
Watch the goals and highlights as Real Madrid became UEFA Super Cup 2024 champions after defeating Atalanta 2-0 in Warsaw (Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta). Real Madrid have picked up their first piece of silverware of the 2024/25 season thanks to second half goals from Fede Valverde and new signing Kylian Mbappé. Valverde and Mbappé were assisted by Vini Jr. and Jude Bellingham respectively. With this victory, club captain Luka Modrić became the most decorated player in Real Madrid's history with 27 titles.

es.title: RESUMEN | Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta | Supercopa de Europa 2024
es.description:
Disfruta de los goles y de los mejores momentos de la final de la Supercopa de Europa 2024, en la que el Real Madrid se coronó como campeón tras derrotar a la Atalanta por 2-0 en Varsovia (Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta). El Real Madrid ha conseguido su primer título de la temporada 2024/25 gracias a los goles de Fede Valverde y del nuevo fichaje Kylian Mbappé, tras asistencias de Vini Jr. y Jude Bellingham respectivamente. Con esta victoria, el capitán Luka Modrić, se convirtió en el jugador más condecorado de la historia del Real Madrid con 27 títulos.
#6SuperCups

en.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta | UEFA Super Cup 2024
en.description:
Watch the goals and highlights as Real Madrid became UEFA Super Cup 2024 champions after defeating Atalanta 2-0 in Warsaw (Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta). Real Madrid have picked up their first piece of silverware of the 2024/25 season thanks to second half goals from Fede Valverde and new signing Kylian Mbappé. Valverde and Mbappé were assisted by Vini Jr. and Jude Bellingham respectively. With this victory, club captain Luka Modrić became the most decorated player in Real Madrid's history with 27 titles.
#6SuperCups
